Was looking over Ryze to see about re-learning him and say Young Ryze. Was all, &quot;Oh damn, I like that, lets go see what it costs.&quot;

Only available if you preordered the retail edition back in 2009.

And I&#039;m just... ugh. Got my interest piqued, then dashed. If it was a Legacy skin that could come back at some point it&#039;d be one thing, but the skins that aren&#039;t ever going to be back like that? I&#039;d rather have not had it advertised to me like that at all, to be honest.
